22 August 2019: Version 1.1
-Added character analysis to give suggestions based on frequency rather than a 
brute-force decrement. This reduces the number of attempts to convert the
cipher "Zdrxzerkzfe zj dfiv zdgfikrek kyre Befncvuxv" to "Imagination is more 
important than Knowledge" from 17 to 4.

22 August 2019: Version 1.1.1
-Changed how characters are detected to avoid modifying non-alphabetic characters.

26 August 2019: Version 1.1.2
-Added variable for if a letter was upper or lowercase, to fix a bug where a
character's case may inadvertantly change if the offset left it as a valid
ASCII letter.